description:
What: Add new JSON-RPC parameter/result structs to core/src/protocol.rs for the guild/channel API.

Algorithm:
1. Read /home/mark/PROJECT/Agora/core/src/protocol.rs to understand existing structure
2. Add new constants to the rpc_methods module:
   pub const GUILD_CREATE: &str = "guild.create";
   pub const GUILD_LIST: &str = "guild.list";
   pub const GUILD_GET: &str = "guild.get";
   pub const GUILD_JOIN: &str = "guild.join";
   pub const GUILD_LEAVE: &str = "guild.leave";
   pub const CHANNEL_CREATE: &str = "channel.create";
   pub const CHANNEL_LIST: &str = "channel.list";
   pub const CHANNEL_GET: &str = "channel.get";
   pub const GUILD_STATE_UPDATE: &str = "guild.state_update";  // notification: new guild state available

3. Add parameter/result structs:

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct GuildCreateParams { pub name: String, pub description: Option<String> }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct GuildCreateResult { pub guild_cid: String }  // CIDv1 of genesis GuildState

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct GuildGetParams { pub guild_cid: String }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct GuildGetResult { pub guild_cid: String, pub state_json: String }  -- raw signed GuildState JSON

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct GuildListResult { pub guilds: Vec<GuildInfo> }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct GuildInfo { pub guild_cid: String, pub name: String, pub owner: String }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct GuildJoinParams { pub guild_cid: String }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct GuildLeaveParams { pub guild_cid: String }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct ChannelCreateParams { pub guild_cid: String, pub path: String, pub name: String, pub mode: String }  // mode: "interactive"|"community"|"broadcast"

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct ChannelCreateResult { pub channel_cid: String, pub guild_cid: String, pub path: String }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct ChannelListParams { pub guild_cid: String }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct ChannelListResult { pub channels: Vec<ChannelInfo> }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct ChannelInfo { pub channel_cid: String, pub path: String, pub name: String, pub mode: String }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct ChannelGetParams { pub guild_cid: String, pub path: String }

   #[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, Debug)]
   pub struct ChannelGetResult { pub channel_cid: String, pub state_json: String }

4. Run cargo check -p agora-core 2>&1

Defensive: Structs use Option<> for optional fields. No unwrap(). All fields snake_case (serde auto-derives).
Report: pass/fail. List all new constants and struct names.
